{"ID":"20260305082131-9bzgyao","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9bzgyao","tags":"课程/CPP程序设计","title":"多继承","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-t5chk1o","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-t5chk1o"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 多继承\ndate created: 星期三, 十月 22日 2025, 8:50:56 早上\ndate modified: 星期三, 十月 22日 2025, 2:51:41 下午\ntags:\n  - 课程/CPP程序设计\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-5uk8l59","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-5uk8l59","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 多继承"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-dr6gpd3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-dr6gpd3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如右图所示，即为多继承。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-tynu2vd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tynu2vd","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"![[继承-1.png]]"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1h5v36c","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1h5v36c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"Class ClassName : \u003c派生控制\u003e Base1,\n\t\t    \t  //...\n\t\t\t\t  \u003c派生控制\u003e Basen\n{\n//...\n};\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1lbh9v8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1lbh9v8","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同一个类不能多次作为某个派生类的直接基类，可以多次作为一个类的间接基类（比如包含一个该类的成员对象，或链式继承）。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-1w5xdtl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-1w5xdtl","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 构造函数、派生类对象的构造和析构顺序"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-8cxbdeb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-8cxbdeb","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"构造顺序"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-zi75as4","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-zi75as4","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"struct A { \n\tint a;\n\tA(int a) { \n\t\tthis-\u003ea = a; \n\t\tcout \u003c\u003c \"a= \"\u003c\u003ca\u003c\u003cendl; \n\t}\n};\n\nstruct B : public A { \n\tint b;\n\tB(int b) : A(3) {\n\t\tB::b = b; \n\t\tcout \u003c\u003c\"b = \"\u003c\u003cb\u003c\u003cendl; \n\t}\n};\n\nstruct C : public A { \n\tint c;\n\tC(int c) : A(5) {\n\t\tC::c = c; \n\t\tcout \u003c\u003c\"c = \"\u003c\u003cc\u003c\u003cendl; \n\t}\n};\n\nstruct D : public B, public C { \n\tint d;\n\tD(int b,int c,int d) : C(c), B(b) {\n\t\tD::d = d; \n\t\tcout \u003c\u003c\"d = \"\u003c\u003cd\u003c\u003cendl; \n\t}\n\n};\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-yh1ux56","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-yh1ux56","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"![[继承-2.png|350]]"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lv3qwh2","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lv3qwh2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ifwwwjn","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ifwwwjn","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-xjmy5ky","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xjmy5ky","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"建立一棵派生树。其结点的顺序为：按定义派生类时基类出现的顺序，从左到右。若类中\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e声明了对象作为成员\u003c/font\u003e，则以该对象为\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e根\u003c/font\u003e再\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e构造另一颗派生树\u003c/font\u003e。 ^3e396a"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c1vqol2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c1vqol2","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-63rqtdi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-63rqtdi","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对象构造时的顺序为：按树的\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e后序遍历\u003c/font\u003e访问结点的原则，确定构造顺序。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-6jmqy0x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6jmqy0x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若将 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"struct D"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的定义改为："}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xdbqyx0","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xdbqyx0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"struct D : public B { \n\tC objc;\n\tint d;\n};\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-3i9fgo1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-3i9fgo1","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其内存空间则变为："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"![[继承-3.png|350]]"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-drk2qck","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-drk2qck","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"析构顺序："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 与构造顺序相反。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9mhkgwk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9mhkgwk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 多继承带来的问题"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0jgslsq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0jgslsq","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如图所示的继承方式带来了一些问题："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"![[继承-4.png|350]]"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-v9g38nm","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-v9g38nm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-tnve18u","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-tnve18u","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ioykqxx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ioykqxx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当对象成员和基类\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e存在共同的基类\u003c/font\u003e时，就可能对同一个物理对象\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e重复初始化\u003c/font\u003e（可能是危险的和不必要的）；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-c35j6he","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-c35j6he","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-g8mlblk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-g8mlblk","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多继承不能解决同一个物理对象初始化多次的问题；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7bud0cx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7bud0cx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-h9jvxki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h9jvxki","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以采用全局变量、静态数据成员，解决同一个物理对象初始化两次的问题，但解决相关析构问题复杂。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-7974tn3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-7974tn3","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们希望类 D 只拥有一个类 A，于是，引入了 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082131-flcaji7","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"虚基类"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 实现了两个对象共享一个物理对象的需求。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4sku321","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4sku321","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4 多继承类的内存布局"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-4j8nxm0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-4j8nxm0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"多继承派生类包含各个基类的存储空间。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-57abfx0","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-57abfx0","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-h0g7tb7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-h0g7tb7","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-6u24gjx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-6u24gjx","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果存在虚基类和同名基类，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082131-flcaji7","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"虚基类"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和同名基类的存储空间是相互独立的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-9ny6r3m","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9ny6r3m","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-ep0cury","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-ep0cury","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果派生类存在同名的虚基类，同一棵派生树的所有虚基类共享存储空间，虚基类通过偏移指向共享存储空间，该存储空间出现在所有直接基类之后。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-vjr288w","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-vjr288w","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-9h85jpm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-9h85jpm","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果基类或派生类存在虚函数，则在派生类存储空间中，包含一个单元存放虚函数入口地址表首地址。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-0o67syg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-0o67syg","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-kwgf37x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-kwgf37x","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"派生类的存储空间不包括基类、虚基类和对象成员的静态数据成员。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-lb32n55","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-lb32n55","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"派生类有 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082131-flcaji7","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"虚基类"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的情况下的详解："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虚基类的存储空间建于派生类的尾部，且按虚基类的构造顺序建立。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-pgsrrw6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-pgsrrw6","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-cwzc72c","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-cwzc72c","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-okr8zkf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-okr8zkf","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"派生类依次处理每个直接基类或虚基类，如果为直接基类，则为其建立存储空间，如果为直接虚基类则建立一个到虚基类的偏移。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082131-xcwvuex","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-xcwvuex","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082131-p9fmnto","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-p9fmnto","updated":"20260305082131"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果派生类继承的第一个类为非虚基类，且该基类定义了虚函数地址表，则派生类就共享该表首址占用的存储单元。对于其他任何情形，派生类在处理完所有基类或虚基类后，根据派生类是否新定义了虚函数，确定是否为该表首址分配存储单元。"}]}]}]}]}